Kundan Mehta, is a retired nurse. She is affluent and wants
to live independently. She loves watching Hindi movies
and her favourite actor is Rishi Kapoor. She is happy
spending time with her friends here in the old age home,
but craves to meet her family members. She is suffering
from dementia and is scared to walk alone. It is difficult for
her to keep track of her medicines and panics when the
caretaker of the old age home does not respond
